{
  "page": "Theo Wull",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wull\" title=\"House Wull\"><img alt=\"House Wull.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/50px-House_Wull.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/75px-House_Wull.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/100px-House_Wull.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Theo Wull<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Buckets</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wull\" title=\"House Wull\"><img alt=\"House Wull.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/50px-House_Wull.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/75px-House_Wull.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0e/House_Wull.svg/100px-House_Wull.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Theo_Wull_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Theo Wull TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c6/Theo_Wull_TheMico.jpg/350px-Theo_Wull_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"/images/c/c6/Theo_Wull_TheMico.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Theo Wull, by TheMico ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nBuckets</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Wull\" title=\"House Wull\">House Wull</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">Northern mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/283_AC\" title=\"283 AC\">283&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Combat_at_the_tower_of_joy\" title=\"Combat at the tower of joy\">tower of joy</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Buried</th><td>\nthe tower of joy, Dorne</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Theo Wull</b>, also known as <b>Buckets</b> because of his <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">clan's</a> sigil, was a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wull\" title=\"House Wull\">Wulls</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His relation to <a href=\"/index.php/Hugo_Wull\" title=\"Hugo Wull\">Hugo Wull</a>, the clan chief of the Wulls, is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> considers Theo to have been faithful.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Theo was one of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>'s companions, fighting alongside him during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>. He was slain at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tower_of_joy\" title=\"Tower of joy\">tower of joy</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Mountains\" title=\"Red Mountains\">Red Mountains</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Combat_at_the_tower_of_joy\" title=\"Combat at the tower of joy\">during a fight</a> with three of <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>. Afterwards, Eddard had the tower pulled down, and used its stones for cairns for the fallen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During a fever dream, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> recalls Theo and his other former companions at the tower of joy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> and his companions travel through the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">northern mountains</a>. They see almost no-one on their journey, and <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a> asks if anyone lives there. Bran mentions the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">northern mountain clans</a>, including the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wull\" title=\"House Wull\">Wulls</a>, and Meera asks her brother <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen</a> if she recalls correctly that a Wull rode with <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">their father</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>. Jojen replies that it was Theo Wull, called Buckets, and Bran adds that buckets are on House Wull's <a href=\"/index.php/Sigil\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sigil\">sigil</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>In the dream his friends rode with him, as they had in life. Proud <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Cassel\" title=\"Martyn Cassel\">Martyn Cassel</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory</a>'s father; faithful Theo Wull; <a href=\"/index.php/Ethan_Glover\" title=\"Ethan Glover\">Ethan Glover</a>, who had been <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark\" title=\"Brandon Stark\">Brandon</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>; Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mark_Ryswell\" title=\"Mark Ryswell\">Mark Ryswell</a>, soft of speech and gentle of heart; the <a href=\"/index.php/Crannogman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crannogman\">crannogman</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Howland Reed</a>; Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_Dustin\" title=\"Willam Dustin\">Dustin</a> on his great red <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">stallion</a>. Ned had known their faces as well as he knew his own once, but the years leech at a man's memories, even those he has vowed never to forget. In the dream they were only shadows, grey wraiths on horses made of mist.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Meera</b>: Jojen, wasn't there a Wull who rode with <a href=\"/index.php/Howland_Reed\" title=\"Howland Reed\">Father</a> during <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">the war</a>?<br />\n<b>Jojen</b>: Theo Wull. Buckets, they used to call him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Theo_Wull&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_39\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 39\">Chapter 39</a>, Eddard X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403185057\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.275 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1113/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10827/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9909/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1742/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2340/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.74 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  258.613      1 -total\n 93.28%  241.229      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 92.74%  239.844      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.93%   25.670     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.27%   13.619      7 Template:Ref\n  4.41%   11.394      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.33%    8.614      7 Template:Ref/core\n  1.85%    4.772      1 Template:Date\n  1.53%    3.956      2 Template:Quote\n  0.88%    2.271      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:3164-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403185057 and revision id 325799\n -->\n",
